  Returns a map with the keys `:pairs`, `:unmatched_left`, `:unmatched_right` and
  `:duplicate_keys`. The order of entries within each list is unspecified.

  ## Examples

      iex> left = [%{id: 1, v: :a}, %{id: 1, v: :b}]
      iex> right = [%{id: 1, v: :a}]
